		('LOC_FEATURE_SUK_TE_OTUKAPUARANGI_NAME',
		'Te Ōtukapuarangi'),
		('LOC_FEATURE_SUK_TE_OTUKAPUARANGI_DESCRIPTION',
		'Two tile impassable natural wonder. Provides either +1 [ICON_Culture] Culture and +1 [ICON_Food] Food, or +1 [ICON_Science] Science to adjacent tiles, alternating between the two every 20 or so turns. These yields are doubled in Ecstatic cities. Provides Fresh Water.'),
